OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777309554
OL,3,CSinn Fein president says referendum
OL,4,Ccan be achieved by 2030
OL,6,FMary Lou McDonald has urged voters to
OL,7,F"hit" Government parties "harder" by
OL,8,Fsupporting Sinn Fein in upcoming by-
OL,9,Felections in an address focused on
OL,10,Fcost-of-living measures.
OL,12,FIn her speech to party faithful at the
OL,13,FArd Fheis in Belfast, the Sinn Fein
OL,14,Fpresident said the Government needs to
OL,15,Fintroduce an emergency budget after
OL,16,Ftrying to "buy off" fuel protesters.
OL,26,@kD@GrroD@AOUoD@EO]oD@ZOUoD@aO]xD@KOUxD@
OL,26,ASO]
