CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777309554
OL,3,CSinn Fein president says referendum
OL,4,Ccan be achieved by 2030
OL,6,FShe also said an Irish unity
OL,7,Freferendum by 2030 is still possible
OL,8,Fand she hoped unionist political
OL,9,Fleaders would see the "chance of real
OL,10,Fwins".
OL,12,FEarlier on Saturday, Ms McDonald
OL,13,Fsought to play down reports of
OL,14,Fdiscontent with her leadership,
OL,15,Finsisting she will lead Sinn Fein into
OL,16,Fthe next general election and stating
OL,17,Fshe has the confidence of party
OL,18,Fmembers.
OL,26,@kD@GrrqD@WOUrD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
