CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777309554
OL,3,CSinn Fein president says referendum
OL,4,Ccan be achieved by 2030
OL,6,FIn her keynote address, the Sinn Fein
OL,7,Fleader referred to fuel protests that
OL,8,Fbrought parts of Ireland to a
OL,9,Fstandstill, saying people gathered
OL,10,F"with tractors, trucks and lorries `
OL,11,Ftools of their livelihoods".
OL,13,F"Fianna Fail and Fine Gael believed
OL,14,Fthey could buy off workers with half-
OL,15,Fmeasures, that they had subdued the
OL,16,Fordinary people of Ireland," she said.
OL,18,F"They were wrong.
OL,26,@kD@GrrrD@AOUsD@[O]uD@AOUxD@\O]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777309554
OL,3,CSinn Fein president says referendum
OL,4,Ccan be achieved by 2030
OL,6,F"The people stood up, challenged those
OL,7,Fin power and put them on notice that
OL,8,Fworkers and families can't take any
OL,9,Fmore."
OL,11,FShe reiterated calls on the Government
OL,12,Fto introduce an emergency mini-budget
OL,13,F"with a substantial cut to excise to
OL,14,Fmake fuel affordable, including the
OL,15,Fcomplete removal of carbon tax on home
OL,16,Fheating oil and green diesel" as well
OL,17,Fas electricity credits, additional
OL,18,Fsupport for social welfare and
OL,19,F"immediate relief for taxpayers".
OL,26,@kD@GrrnD@AOUqD@FO]uD@AOUxD@]O]{D@AOU{D@
OL,26,A`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
