CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777309554
OL,3,CSinn Fein president says referendum
OL,4,Ccan be achieved by 2030
OL,6,F"The universal social charge (USC),
OL,7,FFianna Fail's tax, introduced when
OL,8,Fthey crashed the Irish economy, is a
OL,9,Fconstant drag on your wages," she said.
OL,11,F"We are calling for a permanent cut in
OL,12,Fthis tax for every worker, starting
OL,13,Fwith putting 500 euro back in your
OL,14,Fpocket.
OL,16,F"This must happen now because people
OL,17,Fcannot wait."
OL,26,@kD@GrrnD@AOUqD@]O]sD@AOUxD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
