OL,3,CSinn Fein president says referendum
OL,4,Ccan be achieved by 2030
OL,6,FMoving to Irish unity, Ms McDonald
OL,7,Fsaid a referendum can be achieved by
OL,8,F2030 but "preparation must happen now"
OL,9,Fas she made a direct appeal to
OL,10,Funionist politicians in Northern
OL,11,FIreland.
OL,13,F"We respect and value Protestant,
OL,14,Funionist, loyalist people ` this is
OL,15,Fyour home and we want to build
OL,16,FIreland's future with you, to work
OL,17,Fconstructively together," she said.
OL,19,F"The leadership of unionism must work
OL,20,Falso for progress.
OL,26,@kD@GrrpD@JOUpD@fO]uD@AOUyD@YO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777309554
OL,3,CSinn Fein president says referendum
OL,4,Ccan be achieved by 2030
OL,6,F"Divisive, rejectionist, sectarian
OL,7,Fpolitics must be consigned to history,
OL,8,Fit has no place in our future.
OL,10,F"Casement Park will be built, the
OL,11,Fdiggers are on-site. The A5 will save
OL,12,Flives, stopping this road is not
OL,13,Facceptable."
OL,15,FHer harshest critique was reserved for
OL,16,Fthe Government parties, who she said
OL,17,Fare the "biggest barrier to planning
OL,18,Ffor unity".
OL,20,F"The days of saying yes to unity, but
OL,21,F'not now', must end," she said.
OL,26,@kD@GrrnD@AOUrD@AOUuD@LO]yD@IOUzD@JO]|D@
OL,26,AAOU}D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777309554
OL,3,CSinn Fein president says referendum
OL,4,Ccan be achieved by 2030
OL,6,F"They must do what's right for Ireland
OL,7,F` lead, prepare for referendums,
OL,8,Fengage with people, grasp the
OL,9,Fopportunity of the united island.
OL,11,F"That is the patriotic thing to do."
OL,13,FShe added: "Make no mistake, we are
OL,14,Fout to fully end British government
OL,15,Frule in Ireland."
OL,26,@kD@GrrnD@AOUsD@AOUsD@dO]uD@LOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
