CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777309554
OL,3,CSinn Fein president says referendum
OL,4,Ccan be achieved by 2030
OL,6,FThe Sinn Fein president took aim at
OL,7,Fthe Government's housing policy,
OL,8,Fdescribing them as "the parties of
OL,9,Fboarded-up homes, rip-off rents, sky-
OL,10,Fhigh house prices, of chronic
OL,11,Fhomelessness, robbing families of
OL,12,Fdignity, children of childhood.
OL,14,F"We cannot, we will not allow them to
OL,15,Fprevail."
OL,17,FMs McDonald received one of her
OL,18,Fstrongest responses from the crowd
OL,19,Fwhen referring to the war in the
OL,20,FMiddle East, saying Israel needs to be
OL,21,Fshown "the red card".
OL,26,@kD@GrrpD@TOUvD@AOUwD@IO]}D@GOU}D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777309554
OL,3,CSinn Fein president says referendum
OL,4,Ccan be achieved by 2030
OL,6,F"No whitewashing, no sports washing,
OL,7,Fno welcome for the Israeli football
OL,8,Fteam," she said.
OL,10,FMs McDonald said: "Micheal Martin,
OL,11,FSimon Harris, I challenge you to put
OL,12,Fyour plans to scrap the triple lock to
OL,13,Fthe people. You'll get your answer.
OL,14,FHands off Irish neutrality."
OL,16,FIn her concluding remarks, she told
OL,17,Fmembers: "Fianna Fail and Fine Gael
OL,18,Fmay have survived Sinn Fein's motion
OL,19,Fof no confidence, but they do not have
OL,20,Fthe confidence of the Irish people.
OL,26,@kD@GrrnD@AOUpD@FO]rD@SOUvD@\O]yD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777309554
OL,3,CSinn Fein president says referendum
OL,4,Ccan be achieved by 2030
OL,6,F"They have lost a minister and a TD,
OL,7,Ftwo men down.
OL,9,F"We were strong enough to take them on
OL,10,Fand we forced the first cracks in this
OL,11,FGovernment, but we need to keep the
OL,12,Fpressure on because we need to get
OL,13,Fthem out.
OL,15,F"The upcoming by-elections are your
OL,16,Fchance to hit them harder, to
OL,17,Fstrengthen Sinn Fein's hand."
OL,26,@kD@GrrnD@AOUqD@AOUwD@AOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
