PN,44612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777309554
OL,3,CSinn Fein president says referendum
OL,4,Ccan be achieved by 2030
OL,6,FAt the conclusion of her speech she
OL,7,Fjoined party members in singing Amhran
OL,8,Fna bhFiann, the Irish national anthem,
OL,9,Fwhich was followed by Do You Hear The
OL,10,FPeople Sing from the musical Les
OL,11,FMiserables.
OL,13,FOn Saturday morning, flagged by party
OL,14,Fcolleagues from both sides of the
OL,15,Fborder including First Minister
OL,16,FMichelle O'Neill, Ms McDonald sought
OL,17,Fto pour cold water on reports of
OL,18,Fdesire for a change of leader.
OL,26,@kD@Grr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777309554
OL,3,CSinn Fein president says referendum
OL,4,Ccan be achieved by 2030
OL,6,FSpeaking to the media, she said:
OL,7,F"We're in a very, very strong
OL,8,Fposition, so we go out and we fight
OL,9,Fthose elections in that spirit."
OL,11,F"I'm very proud to lead this party.
OL,12,FI'm very proud to enjoy the confidence
OL,13,Fof my colleagues and the broader
OL,14,Fmembership. So, as you may try to seek
OL,15,Fa story in that, there isn't a story
OL,16,Fthere.
OL,18,F"I'm the leader of the party, we are a
OL,19,Fcollective leadership and we are in a
OL,20,Fvery, very good place.
OL,26,@kD@GrroD@AOUqD@`O]sD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777309554
OL,3,CSinn Fein president says referendum
OL,4,Ccan be achieved by 2030
OL,6,F"So, we'll fight the by-elections and
OL,7,FI think they're going to be
OL,8,Ffascinating contests, actually, in
OL,9,Fboth constituencies. I think it'll be
OL,10,Fa brave person who would predict the
OL,11,Foutcomes of them."
OL,13,FAsked directly if she would lead Sinn
OL,14,FFein into the next general election,
OL,15,Fshe said: "Yes."
OL,17,FThe crowd cheered and applauded before
OL,18,FMs McDonald's keynote address when it
OL,19,Fwas announced that she was re-elected
OL,20,Fas president.
OL,26,@kD@GrrnD@AOUsD@RO]wD@KOUwD@PO]
